title: THURSDAY 5/6 - AARON RODGERS UNHAPPY IN GREEN BAY
itunes:title: THURSDAY 5/6 - AARON RODGERS UNHAPPY IN GREEN BAY
description:
More drama from the Aaron Rodgers situation in Green Bay. Former Packers QB Brett Favre (0:32) gives his take on the situation. As for Rodgers (0:59), Mike Garafolo say his unhappiness goes back to before the start of the season. Dak Prescott (1:28) says he's ready to take the field again, and new Ravens offensive lineman Alejandro Villanueva (1:58) throws some shade at his former team
